dc_title_s: Congressional Districts: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2014
dc_description_s: This coverage represents the Board of Elections approved boundaries of the Congressional Districts partially or entirely within Prince George's County. While this coverage is maintained by the Prince George's County GIS Section, the boundaries are defined and its representation approved by the Board of Elections. This layer was last updated in May 23, 2013 and compiled at 1:2,400.
